videos.headline: LA Tech's Dancy scores third TD of the day
videos.description: Jaqwis Dancy rushes 18 yards for his third touchdown of the night for LA Tech.

videos.headline: Rice's Walter scores 68-yard TD
videos.description: Austin Walter catches the pass and slips away from the clutches of a LA Tech defender to score a 68-yard Rice touchdown.
